    "This necessitates the development of specific prompts for GPT to enable a fair comparison of entity extraction performance between the two models These methods allow models to efficiently learn and adapt from a limited set of examples, which is ideal in scenarios such as healthcare documentation, where extensive data collection is often impractical or impossible.",
